  "ABOUT": {
    "LEAD": "At the end of October, dozens of academic conferences will be held across the country in a wide range of research fields, as part of an initiative to strengthen ties between Israeli researchers and research institutions, both in Israel and abroad.",
    "CONTENT_1": "The initiative, in collaboration with <strong>the Israel Young Academy</strong>, seeks to leverage the arrival of thousands of Israeli researchers from abroad to Israel during the Knesset election period to create professional meetings, encourage research collaborations, reveal new academic opportunities, and strengthen the international status of Israeli academia.",
    "CONTENT_2": "Mind-IL invites researchers and industry partners to take part in a celebration of scientific excellence, creativity, and international cooperation.",
